# Universal PPI Builder (BioGRID ‚Üí Cytoscape)

**Author:** Armaghan Moradi  
**Language:** R  
**Purpose:** Build clean protein‚Äìprotein interaction (PPI) networks from BioGRID and differential gene expression (DEG) data for Cytoscape visualization.

---

üß† Features
- Works with any project (e.g., Neuroblastoma, Osteosarcoma, etc.)
- Reads DEGs from Excel (Up/Down-regulated)
- Extracts matching interactions from BioGRID
- Computes centrality metrics (degree, betweenness, closeness)
- Outputs Cytoscape-ready edge and node tables
- Automatically builds ‚Äúcore + first neighbor‚Äù subnetworks

